SUMMARY:Rules-Light RPGs
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nChange your PRIVACY SETTINGS so I can actually reply to your messages! :)\nor contact me directly at\nemail = [God.Emperor@Gmail.com](http://God.Emperor@gmail.com/)\ncall/text = 971 325-2100\n\nJoin us on Tuesday for Kids on Bikes\, Super Spies\, Escape from Dino Island\, Spacy weird Fantasy\, Mörk Borg/Pirates\, or Call of Cthulhu\, and other Homebrew One-Shots -- things change over time.\n\nSo send me an email at [God.Emperor@Gmail.com](http://God.Emperor@gmail.com/) or call/text me at 971 325-2100 for more setting and system info. And the story plots are episodic enough that you can miss sessions and it's no big deal.
